Counter Strike: Global Offensive.
A whole new experience and a different kind of First Person Shooter.
In this game you will find:
-Strategy;
-Cheaters;
-Toxic People;
-Smurfs;
-and piercing shots.
It's worth to try it out if you haven't yet. If you are sick of just running and shooting and you were looking for a FPS with tactics, strategic plays and to be patient you did find the game you're looking for because CS:GO will make you play with him for hours. This is a fun experience and also a frustrating one but when you get used to it you will feel like you are improving and you will until you find harder enemies again. But once again it's worth it. Don't be left out of the group that plays CS:GO give it a try.
9/10 it's not perfect but it's one of the only games you will find like this.

Good luck and be positive. Have a blessed day.Stay with God.
